- @title = "Please update your web browser (417)"
%h1
  Oh dear. Your web browser is too buggy for the latest version of Loomio.
%p
  How would you like to proceed?
  %ul
    %li
      Upgrade your browser 🚀
      Use your "system update" feature, or install
      %a{href: "http://firefox.com"} Firefox,
      or
      %a{href: "https://google.com/chrome"} Chrome,
      or even consider using another device you have handy 📱
    %li
      %a{href: "/dashboard?old_client=1"} Use the old Loomio 🗝️
      (it won't be around much longer)
    %li
      Ignore warnings and
      %a{href: "/dashboard?skip_browser_upgrade=1"} use Loomio 2 with current browser ⚠️

%p
  Good luck! 💁‍♂️
